@startuml
title UML State Chart Diagram

[*] --> Login

state Login
Login : entry / getInfo
Login : do / verifyData
Login : exit / verified

state MainMenu <<choice>>
Login --> MainMenu

state MarketConditions
MarketConditions : entry / select option
MarketConditions : do / show market conditions
MarketConditions : exit / display report

state PestControl
PestControl : entry / select option
PestControl : do / require photo
PestControl : exit / capture photo

state PhotoCapture
PhotoCapture : entry / provide photo
PhotoCapture : do / verify photo
PhotoCapture : exit / show techniques

state MarketReport
MarketReport : entry / display report
MarketReport : do / user review
MarketReport : exit / continue or logout

state PestTechniques
PestTechniques : entry / display techniques
PestTechniques : do / review techniques
PestTechniques : exit / continue or logout

state SoilInfo
SoilInfo : entry / select option
SoilInfo : do / provide soil
@enduml
